1
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:39,260
Mast! Lay down the mast!

2
00:00:44,660 --> 00:00:46,900
Hurry up and get the rope!

3
00:00:48,220 --> 00:00:50,900
Bow and stern face the banks! Quick!

4
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:56,980
Thousands of homes are brightly lit,

5
00:00:56,980 --> 00:00:59,420
and the doors to them are wide open.

6
00:00:59,420 --> 00:01:01,580
This is East Capital.

7
00:01:02,220 --> 00:01:05,180
New wine from Sunyang Restaurant!

8
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:07,700
Welcome to enjoy it!

9
00:01:07,860 --> 00:01:10,380
If you want to know what happens next,

10
00:01:10,380 --> 00:01:12,460
wait until next time.

11
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:14,980
People from all over the world gather here,

12
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:17,940
and envoys from various countries come to communicate with the authorities.

13
00:01:22,340 --> 00:01:24,660
[Riverside Code at Qingming Festival]

14
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,660
[Adapted from Ye Wenbiao's Novel Series of the Same Name]

15
00:01:27,140 --> 00:01:27,980
[Episode 25]

16
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:28,980
[One should reflect on the world between rulers and subordinates,]

17
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:29,760
[parents and children, brothers and sisters, and husbands and wives]

18
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,480
[to see how many fall short in fulfilling their roles.]

19
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:30,960
[Cheng Hao from Northern Song Dynasty]

20
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,630
You must wish for a world

21
00:01:33,190 --> 00:01:33,780
where people like you,

22
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,120
like me,

23
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:36,270
like Wen Yue,

24
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:39,080
like Sun Bo and Song Qiyu

25
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:40,910
would suffer less.

26
00:01:41,250 --> 00:01:41,800
I do.

27
00:01:43,810 --> 00:01:44,800
Of course, I do.

28
00:01:47,590 --> 00:01:48,370
I knew it.

29
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,270
You, like Mr. Song,

30
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,680
are concerned about the whole country.

31
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,310
We still have a chance.

32
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,370
All we need is...

33
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:56,590
A chance?

34
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,450
Mr. Song sacrificed himself

35
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:03,400
to expose the exam fraud to the public.

36
00:02:03,630 --> 00:02:05,040
Sun Bo gave his life

37
00:02:05,510 --> 00:02:07,510
to destroy the evil forces controlling the property agency,

38
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:09,520
bringing a measure of justice to the people.

39
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,600
Ci gave her all

40
00:02:13,550 --> 00:02:15,160
to uncover the crimes of Yayuan Mansion.

41
00:02:16,190 --> 00:02:17,320
Justice and fairness

42
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,800
always come at a price.

43
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,960
I'm not afraid to pay that price!

44
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:31,030
Look at this tiny fishbone.

45
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,320
Though small,

46
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,860
if it gets stuck in the villain's throat,

47
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,160
it can still make him choke.

48
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:54,960
I'm willing to be that bone.

49
00:02:56,830 --> 00:02:58,270
Zou Mian's ship carrying the rare stone

50
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,030
will pass under Rainbow Bridge tomorrow,

51
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:03,030
entering through the East Water Gate,

52
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:04,030
heading to meet the Emperor.

53
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,730
If he meets the Emperor

54
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,220
and regains his power,

55
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,320
our pursuit of justice and fairness

56
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,160
will never come true

57
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,240
in this lifetime.

58
00:03:26,550 --> 00:03:28,110
So, let's ensure Zou Mian's ship

59
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,550
never crosses Rainbow Bridge.

60
00:03:42,190 --> 00:03:43,240
Lady Wen, you're here.

61
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:48,750
Wen Yue?

62
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,160
Wen Yue,

63
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:53,270
why are you here?

64
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:55,600
I wanted to kill Zou Mian,

65
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:57,960
but I failed.

66
00:03:58,960 --> 00:03:59,470
Oh...

67
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,440
Are you okay?

68
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:04,960
I...

69
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,110
I'm fine.

70
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:07,340
Wen Yue,

71
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,210
I'm sorry.

72
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,370
I shouldn't have pushed you into seeking revenge.

73
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:15,440
We've just reunited as siblings.

74
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,810
Don't do anything so dangerous again.

75
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:21,790
But Luan Hui and his wife are dead,

76
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:23,850
so there's no one left to testify against Zou Mian.

77
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,340
Once the rare stone reaches the imperial palace,

78
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,920
he'll likely regain the Emperor's favor.

79
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,950
By then,

80
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:32,260
all your plans

81
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,210
will fall apart.

82
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,600
I don't care.

83
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,640
I've already lost all my family.

84
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:42,480
I cannot lose you too.

85
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,160
That old villain Zou Mian

86
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,040
will get what he deserves one day.

87
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,160
He's not worth risking your life for.

88
00:04:52,350 --> 00:04:53,110
I won't allow

89
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,950
anything to happen to you again.

90
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:58,070
Do you really think so?

91
00:05:03,670 --> 00:05:04,320
Wen Yue,

92
00:05:06,070 --> 00:05:07,880
can you make me a meal?

93
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,000
Just for me.

94
00:05:10,670 --> 00:05:11,270
Sure.

95
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,950
I'll make it for you.

96
00:05:13,610 --> 00:05:14,440
That's great!

97
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:16,390
Can you do it tomorrow?

98
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:17,840
Sure.

99
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,010
I'll do it tomorrow.

100
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,490
Buyou,

101
00:05:42,510 --> 00:05:44,020
I was worried Father hadn't eaten,

102
00:05:45,230 --> 00:05:48,270
so I asked Yao He to make a few dishes.

103
00:05:52,670 --> 00:05:54,320
Wen Yue isn't home,

104
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,700
but I'm here.

105
00:05:55,700 --> 00:05:57,200
I can cook for Father.

106
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,200
It's fine.

107
00:05:59,550 --> 00:06:00,650
If you can get Yao He to help,

108
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:01,670
it works too.

109
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:03,160
Then, during this time,

110
00:06:03,790 --> 00:06:05,640
just ask Yao He to help out.

111
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:08,440
Okay.

112
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,830
Is there food for me?

113
00:06:11,230 --> 00:06:12,390
Yes, there is!

114
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:13,000
Great.

115
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,550
There is.

116
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:27,950
Buyou.

117
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,670
I understand your situation.

118
00:06:35,670 --> 00:06:37,760
If we all know Wen Yue's situation,

119
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:40,460
this family will fall apart.

120
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,180
Pretending we know nothing

121
00:06:44,670 --> 00:06:46,230
is the only way to live in peace.

122
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:50,320
Don't worry.

123
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:52,920
As long as I'm here

124
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,600
and Wen Yue is here,

125
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:56,350
this family won't break apart.

126
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:02,040
Buyou,

127
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:04,550
when is Wen Yue coming back?

128
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,510
Soon.

129
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:10,740
Wen Yue

130
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:13,720
just has some personal matters.

131
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,780
Once they're resolved, she'll return.

132
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:18,920
The key is

133
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:21,280
making that old villain Zou Mian pay.

134
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,480
Making him pay...

135
00:07:27,010 --> 00:07:27,920
Do you have a plan?

136
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:28,830
No,

137
00:07:29,550 --> 00:07:30,220
I'm still thinking.

138
00:07:30,930 --> 00:07:32,000
But I'll come up with something soon.

139
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:37,360
Let's call Father to eat.

140
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:39,480
I'm hungry too.

141
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:40,180
Alright.

142
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,650
Father!

143
00:07:44,350 --> 00:07:45,070
Time to eat!

144
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,530
Time to eat, Father!

145
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:48,820
Father?

146
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:50,510
Buyou,

147
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:51,720
Father's not here.

148
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:52,790
Look.

149
00:07:52,790 --> 00:07:54,230
- Did he go out? - He left this behind.

150
00:07:58,270 --> 00:07:59,270
What a man!

151
00:08:00,110 --> 00:08:02,200
Why does he keep making trouble?

152
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:05,000
Farewell letter...

153
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:06,040
Read the second part.

154
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,200
Do you understand what he would do?

155
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,550
[Farewell Letter]
Brothel...

156
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:12,230
"You ungrateful children!

157
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:15,390
Recent troubles have plagued our family.

158
00:08:15,510 --> 00:08:16,880
Sibling disputes,

159
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,320
and marital discord.

160
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:20,350
As the head of the family,

161
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,480
I've disgraced our ancestors.

162
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,830
I have no face to live on.

163
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:29,040
Since I must leave,

164
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:31,070
I'll do so freely and happily.

165
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:33,520
I've decided to spend all our wealth,

166
00:08:33,790 --> 00:08:36,670
visiting every brothel in East Capital,

167
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:40,440
drinking priceless wine when awake,

168
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:43,200
and resting on beauties' laps when drunk.

169
00:08:43,910 --> 00:08:45,080
To die under flowers

170
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,480
and I'll be a carefree ghost..."

171
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,030
Have some fun...

172
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:48,230
"Don't miss me."

173
00:08:48,470 --> 00:08:49,000
Buyou,

174
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,840
I heard the Emperor once bought wine here

175
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,200
to host a banquet for his ministers.

176
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,620
Yes.

177
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:55,880
Money flows here like water,

178
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,840
spent so fast that you don't even hear a splash.

179
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,470
- Sir, you're here. - Could Father really be here?

180
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,710
Have some fun...

181
00:09:01,180 --> 00:09:02,140
Look at how serious he seems.

182
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:03,670
If he really is here,

183
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:05,030
then he has no sense of propriety.

184
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,550
Drink up!

185
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:09,640
Refill it!

186
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,320
Here, refill it for me!

187
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,840
Start!

188
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,650
Is that our father?

189
00:09:18,620 --> 00:09:19,090
It looks like him,

190
00:09:19,290 --> 00:09:20,110
but I'm not sure.

191
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,030
Let's go in and check.

192
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:26,400
My little peach...

193
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:28,000
I caught one...

194
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,030
I caught one!

195
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:31,000
Another one!

196
00:09:32,230 --> 00:09:32,760
Don't move!

197
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,880
Why are you here?

198
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,320
Go back!

199
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,520
Go back, both of you!

200
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,200
Shh.

201
00:09:40,670 --> 00:09:42,000
I didn't summon you here.

202
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:43,350
Hurry and leave!

203
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:45,150
Come on!

204
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,640
Sir,

205
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:48,960
are you together?

206
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:51,080
Shall I prepare another room for you?

207
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:52,110
- No need. - No, thanks.

208
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,200
Madam,

209
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:54,790
may I ask

210
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:56,910
how much silver will he need to pay for tonight?

211
00:09:58,450 --> 00:09:59,170
Well,

212
00:09:59,170 --> 00:10:00,350
we don't take silver as payment.

213
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,840
Just using this luxury room

214
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,530
costs ten liang of gold.

215
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:06,790
Alright.

216
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:13,790
I don't have enough money on me.

217
00:10:14,110 --> 00:10:14,760
Here's the plan:

218
00:10:15,170 --> 00:10:15,730
Later,

219
00:10:15,730 --> 00:10:16,930
you take Father away first.

220
00:10:16,930 --> 00:10:17,880
No way.

221
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,150
I can't leave you here alone!

222
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,000
Didn't you hear?

223
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,010
Ten liang of gold!

224
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:24,230
Show some backbone,

225
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,230
and take Father away.

226
00:10:25,230 --> 00:10:26,000
If anything happens,

227
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,760
I'll handle it.

228
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,590
Enough!

229
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:33,710
Don't play any more games tonight!

230
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:35,730
Who is it?

231
00:10:35,730 --> 00:10:36,640
It's nothing.

232
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,910
Let's go home first!

233
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,520
Don't leave!

234
00:10:41,410 --> 00:10:43,320
What's going on?

235
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:44,640
Sir,

236
00:10:44,710 --> 00:10:46,960
are the girls not serving you well?

237
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,280
How can they behave so improperly?

238
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:50,910
Calm down.

239
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:52,790
Come over here.

240
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,000
My daughter

241
00:10:56,740 --> 00:10:58,110
is too spoiled.

242
00:10:58,410 --> 00:11:00,000
She has a bad temper.

243
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:00,940
Come on,

244
00:11:00,940 --> 00:11:02,200
let's go on!

245
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,840
Oh, you're the princess.

246
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,230
What princess?

247
00:11:05,230 --> 00:11:06,080
Nonsense!

248
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,280
What a temper she has!

249
00:11:14,350 --> 00:11:15,470
I already told you...

250
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:16,670
Princess,

251
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:17,910
escort His Majesty

252
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:18,810
back home.

253
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:22,640
- Time to leave. Let's go home! - Ban...

254
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,110
- Ban! - Let's go home!

255
00:11:24,110 --> 00:11:25,110
I've not done having fun!

256
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,230
My little peach.

257
00:11:26,230 --> 00:11:27,030
- It's fine... - Sir.

258
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,280
Take care!

259
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:29,150
My little fairy...

260
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:30,030
Take care!

261
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:30,910
My fairy!

262
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:31,590
Let's go!

263
00:11:31,590 --> 00:11:33,450
- My clothes are still inside. - Forget them!

264
00:11:33,450 --> 00:11:34,280
I've not done having fun!

265
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,470
Sorry about this.

266
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:36,550
Sorry to trouble you.

267
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,550
So,

268
00:11:40,110 --> 00:11:40,960
how much do we owe you?

269
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,320
Please spare us!

270
00:11:43,980 --> 00:11:45,690
You're embarrassing us.

271
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,440
If we have done anything wrong,

272
00:11:47,590 --> 00:11:48,550
please forgive us.

273
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,790
Spare us, Sir!

274
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,000
Please!

275
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:54,880
All of you,

276
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,200
sorry for the intrusion.

277
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:08,230
Not a single coin was spent?

278
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,400
I don't understand it either.

279
00:12:12,790 --> 00:12:15,150
That madam even called me a princess.

280
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,790
Could they really have mistaken Father

281
00:12:17,790 --> 00:12:18,960
for the Emperor?

282
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,350
What's strange about that?

283
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:24,960
We are of the same royal bloodline.

284
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,880
That Eleventh Brother.

285
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:29,230
When he was young, he was reckless and carefree,

286
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:31,150
just like me.

287
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:33,520
Father, could you explain in detail?

288
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:34,640
Does he resemble you

289
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:36,880
in behavior or in appearance?

290
00:12:38,710 --> 00:12:40,230
A bit of both.

291
00:12:40,640 --> 00:12:41,400
Back then,

292
00:12:41,590 --> 00:12:43,440
when Eleventh Brother was the Prince of Duan,

293
