00:24:29,470 --> 00:24:30,310
Don't turn around.

583
00:24:30,520 --> 00:24:31,520
Let me handle this.

584
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:36,640
Zou Mian, how dare you!

585
00:24:37,430 --> 00:24:38,950
His Majesty wants to see you,

586
00:24:39,230 --> 00:24:40,680
and you're still not coming down immediately?

587
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:53,830
Father,

588
00:24:54,830 --> 00:24:55,640
insult him.

589
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:58,310
You scoundrel!

590
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:00,710
Still not coming down immediately?

591
00:25:01,110 --> 00:25:02,400
Insult him with authority!

592
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:04,310
You scoundrel!

593
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:05,590
He seems

594
00:25:06,070 --> 00:25:07,880
a bit different

595
00:25:08,560 --> 00:25:10,110
from the last time I saw the Emperor.

596
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:12,800
Is he here?

597
00:25:13,560 --> 00:25:14,640
Can we

598
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:17,230
get a glimpse of His Majesty's face?

599
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:19,040
Zou Mian, how dare you!

600
00:25:19,430 --> 00:25:21,110
Today, the Emperor graces you with His presence,

601
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:23,470
yet you're being so insolent!

602
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:24,590
Father, retreat!

603
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:26,000
Let's head to the shore first.

604
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:30,680
The raft is moving, heading to the shore.

605
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,000
They're running away?

606
00:25:33,710 --> 00:25:34,800
So it was a trick after all.

607
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:37,800
I'll send someone to capture them immediately.

608
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:39,430
Guards!

609
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:40,560
Capture them!

610
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:42,470
Everyone, get off the bridge!

611
00:25:42,710 --> 00:25:43,880
Have you seen Zhao Mo?

612
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,160
No sign of him anywhere.

613
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:50,000
I'm talking to you, did you hear me?

614
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:52,190
Hey, the one pushing the cart!

615
00:25:52,430 --> 00:25:53,280
Get off the bridge!

616
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:54,880
I'm talking to you,

617
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:55,950
the one pushing the cart!

618
00:25:56,230 --> 00:25:57,190
Get off the bridge immediately!

619
00:25:57,400 --> 00:25:58,190
Tie Chi, Fei Jian,

620
00:25:58,470 --> 00:26:00,230
stop the one pushing the cart!

621
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:01,350
Yes, sir!

622
00:26:06,560 --> 00:26:07,110
Move quickly!

623
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,070
Off the bridge now!

624
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:09,280
What are you doing?

625
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:11,190
Didn't you hear the order?

626
00:26:11,520 --> 00:26:12,400
Off the bridge now!

627
00:26:12,420 --> 00:26:12,880
Get down!

628
00:26:12,950 --> 00:26:13,530
Stop!

629
00:26:15,830 --> 00:26:16,590
Archers, ready!

630
00:26:17,230 --> 00:26:17,760
Quickly!

631
00:26:19,010 --> 00:26:19,610
It's Zhao Mo!

632
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:21,520
Mo!

633
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:22,730
Zhao Mo!

634
00:26:22,730 --> 00:26:23,400
Hurry!

635
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:23,950
Zhao Mo!

636
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:26,800
Put the things down first.

637
00:26:27,250 --> 00:26:28,350
Come on, step off the bridge.

638
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:29,920
I have

639
00:26:30,190 --> 00:26:31,430
six fire bombs here.

640
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:32,950
If I ignite them,

641
00:26:33,190 --> 00:26:34,760
the entire bridge will blow up.

642
00:26:36,070 --> 00:26:37,160
All of you, leave now.

643
00:26:38,190 --> 00:26:38,640
Get down!

644
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,430
Inspector Gu,

645
00:26:39,800 --> 00:26:41,310
let me talk to Mo.

646
00:26:42,230 --> 00:26:43,350
Do you think talking to him now

647
00:26:43,710 --> 00:26:44,470
will make any difference?

648
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:46,760
Mo is young and impulsive.

649
00:26:46,760 --> 00:26:47,230
Get down!

650
00:26:47,230 --> 00:26:48,830
He's taken the wrong path in a moment of panic.

651
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:49,920
Give him a chance.

652
00:26:50,070 --> 00:26:51,230
He'll listen to me.

653
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:52,800
And if he doesn't listen to you?

654
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:54,800
Look at the people below the bridge.

655
00:26:55,020 --> 00:26:56,470
You wouldn't want to harm them, would you?

656
00:26:56,580 --> 00:26:58,000
- Give me the fire striker... - Get down!

657
00:26:59,310 --> 00:27:00,590
If anything happens,

658
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:01,430
I'll take full responsibility.

659
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,190
Can you bear the consequences?

660
00:27:03,190 --> 00:27:05,190
If something goes wrong,

661
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:07,800
the only one who can act is me.

662
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:09,040
Get down!

663
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:10,470
Fine.

664
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:11,230
Alright.

665
00:27:12,180 --> 00:27:13,660
You have only this one chance.

666
00:27:14,230 --> 00:27:15,680
I won't play with the lives

667
00:27:15,680 --> 00:27:16,350
of so many people.

668
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:17,800
If you fail,

669
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:19,190
I will act.

670
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:21,410
Everyone, move back!

671
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:23,070
Thank you.

672
00:27:24,950 --> 00:27:25,800
I'm going with you!

673
00:27:25,800 --> 00:27:26,310
- Ban! - Stay there, Ban!

674
00:27:26,310 --> 00:27:26,880
Zhao Mo...

675
00:27:33,350 --> 00:27:34,160
Wen Yue is here.

676
00:27:42,310 --> 00:27:42,920
Mo,

677
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,230
what are you doing?

678
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:46,430
Don't act rashly.

679
00:27:47,950 --> 00:27:49,000
Listen to me.

680
00:27:50,070 --> 00:27:51,310
Put down the fire striker.

681
00:27:52,430 --> 00:27:53,160
Wen Yue,

682
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:56,520
I'm sorry.

683
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:59,590
Ban and I apologize to you.

684
00:28:02,520 --> 00:28:03,680
Once Zou Mian's ship

685
00:28:04,830 --> 00:28:05,830
arrives,

686
00:28:05,880 --> 00:28:06,950
I'll light the fire bombs,

687
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,160
blow up Rainbow Bridge,

688
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:09,950
and stop the stone from entering the palace.

689
00:28:10,520 --> 00:28:12,110
Then I'll have avenged you.

690
00:28:14,110 --> 00:28:14,920
Mo,

691
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:18,400
I've never held anything against you.

692
00:28:20,350 --> 00:28:21,760
No matter whose child you are,

693
00:28:22,760 --> 00:28:24,160
you're my brother,

694
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:25,950
my family.

695
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:28,880
I never thought about revenge,

696
00:28:29,590 --> 00:28:30,760
and I don't need you

697
00:28:30,760 --> 00:28:31,880
to do anything for me.

698
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:34,160
Listen to me, Zhao Mo.

699
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,400
Put down the fire striker.

700
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:37,590
Now.

701
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:38,760
Stay back, Wen Yue!

702
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:39,430
Don't come any closer!

703
00:28:39,590 --> 00:28:40,160
Don't come any closer...

704
00:28:45,230 --> 00:28:46,590
I'm doing all this

705
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:49,280
not just for you,

706
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:53,950
but also for Sun Bo,

707
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,350
and for Ding Dan.

708
00:28:56,590 --> 00:28:57,880
Against people like them,

709
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:59,470
what else can we do?

710
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:02,160
Is there no justice in this world?

711
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,230
Are the lives of the poor

712
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:05,880
so easily trampled on?

713
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:08,680
They were all victims of Zou Mian.

714
00:29:09,710 --> 00:29:11,590
I once made a pact with Ding Dan

715
00:29:12,230 --> 00:29:13,710
to plead for the people,

716
00:29:15,580 --> 00:29:17,040
to join the government for the common good.

717
00:29:19,650 --> 00:29:21,040
I will be another Detective Dee...

718
00:29:21,090 --> 00:29:22,320
Then I'll be another Zhang Jianzhi!

719
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:25,520
But Zou Mian has committed so many crimes,

720
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:27,800
why has he never been punished?

721
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:29,680
There

722
00:29:30,310 --> 00:29:31,560
is no justice in this world.

723
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:34,430
With my blood, I will stain the rare stone.

724
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:36,830
With my body, I will pave the righteous path!

725
00:29:39,950 --> 00:29:41,560
This is the path I've chosen.

726
00:29:41,710 --> 00:29:42,430
Zhao Mo,

727
00:29:42,430 --> 00:29:43,400
get a hold of yourself.

728
00:29:44,190 --> 00:29:46,040
I don't want to discuss righteousness with you now.

729
00:29:46,300 --> 00:29:47,300
Your life

730
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:50,040
was saved by our father and your brother,

731
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:53,110
and raised by me with ten years of toil!

732
00:29:54,590 --> 00:29:55,680
Your life

733
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:57,470
is meant for something greater!

734
00:29:57,710 --> 00:29:58,710
What's the point of blowing up some stone?

735
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:00,850
Kill one Zou Mian,

736
00:30:00,850 --> 00:30:01,890
and there will be another.

737
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,170
If you're not afraid of death,

738
00:30:03,170 --> 00:30:04,760
then why not live boldly instead?

739
00:30:05,830 --> 00:30:07,590
Step by step, we can change the world.

740
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:13,560
Mo,

741
00:30:15,040 --> 00:30:16,560
I also want to see

742
00:30:17,310 --> 00:30:19,070
the better world you dream of.

743
00:30:21,190 --> 00:30:22,760
Let's face life together.

744
00:30:27,040 --> 00:30:28,190
The ship is almost here.

745
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:30,590
I can't let it all fail now!

746
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:32,470
Wen Yue,

747
00:30:32,950 --> 00:30:34,210
being part of the Zhao family

748
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,710
and being your and Buyou's younger brother

749
00:30:38,310 --> 00:30:39,430
has been enough for me

750
00:30:40,040 --> 00:30:41,110
in this lifetime.

751
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:43,160
Wen Yue, please leave.

752
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:45,260
Please leave now!

753
00:30:45,260 --> 00:30:46,690
I beg you, please leave!

754
00:31:06,280 --> 00:31:07,470
At your coming-of-age ceremony,

755
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,830
you knelt before me,

756
00:31:10,350 --> 00:31:12,470
saying it wasn't easy for me to raise you for ten years

757
00:31:13,110 --> 00:31:15,280
and that half of your life belongs to me.

758
00:31:16,070 --> 00:31:17,950
Doesn't that make me half a mother to you?

759
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:22,560
If you die,

760
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:25,590
how will I go on?

761
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:30,230
If today,

762
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:34,350
you insist on blowing up this bridge,

763
00:31:34,710 --> 00:31:36,110
then I'll stay here with you!

764
00:31:37,070 --> 00:31:39,350
On the path to the afterlife, I'll walk with you!

765
00:31:40,110 --> 00:31:42,230
In the next life, let's be family again!

766
00:31:45,430 --> 00:31:47,560
I beg you, Zhao Mo!

767
00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:12,040
Wen Yue,

768
00:32:15,230 --> 00:32:16,110
I'm sorry.

769
00:32:22,350 --> 00:32:23,310
All right.

770
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:37,950
Wen Yue...

771
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:38,830
Wen Yue...

772
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:52,590
Mo,

773
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:55,350
I'm utterly disappointed in you.

774
00:33:05,950 --> 00:33:06,710
It's over.

775
00:33:11,190 --> 00:33:12,160
Everything is over.

776
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:15,160
Move!

777
00:33:16,830 --> 00:33:17,430
Stop!

778
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:20,710
I have firebombs here.

779
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:23,830
Zheng,

780
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:25,950
you didn't listen to me after all.

781
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,470
You brat, what are you doing?

782
00:33:27,710 --> 00:33:28,800
The ship has already passed!

783
00:33:31,350 --> 00:33:32,000
Wen Yue,

784
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:35,070
How I wish you had come for me.

785
00:33:36,950 --> 00:33:38,430
But alas, you didn't.

786
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:41,760
You think I'm different from Zhao Mo,

787
00:33:42,190 --> 00:33:44,590
so I'll join him and die with that old villain.

788
00:33:45,230 --> 00:33:47,160
But you won't give me this chance.

789
00:33:47,710 --> 00:33:49,190
Do you know how dangerous it is here?

790
00:33:52,830 --> 00:33:54,920
You risked your life to save Mo.

791
00:33:56,350 --> 00:33:58,110
Are you abandoning me again?

792
00:33:58,590 --> 00:34:00,040
Who are you really,

793
00:34:01,710 --> 00:34:02,680
Su Yue or Wen Yue?

794
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:06,760
Who do you truly call family?

795
00:34:07,880 --> 00:34:08,950
My brother

796
00:34:10,470 --> 00:34:11,390
is Su Zheng,

797
00:34:12,600 --> 00:34:13,630
not He Huan.

798
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:14,910
I...

799
00:34:19,390 --> 00:34:21,040
Spare him! Don't shoot!

800
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:28,120
Su Zheng

801
00:34:29,670 --> 00:34:32,040
already died on that fateful road of escape.

802
00:34:34,520 --> 00:34:35,710
For twenty years,

803
00:34:36,230 --> 00:34:38,430
to transport these damned rare stones,

804
00:34:40,910 --> 00:34:42,760
how many laborers have been killed?

805
00:34:43,870 --> 00:34:45,950
How many toilers have died?

806
00:34:48,390 --> 00:34:51,080
The people along the riverbanks have been displaced.

807
00:34:51,430 --> 00:34:52,840
Everywhere these stones pass,

808
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:54,870
they leave behind only bones!

809
00:34:55,470 --> 00:34:56,710
The splendor of the East Capital,

810
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:58,360
the so-called divine blessing,

811
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:01,150
are built upon the blood and tears of the people!

812
00:35:02,470 --> 00:35:03,600
In such a world,

813
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:07,040
only evil can counter evil.

814
00:35:08,230 --> 00:35:09,520
If all those Su Zhengs

815
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,470
had survived,

816
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:15,910
today,

817
00:35:17,670 --> 00:35:19,120
they'd all be He Huan.

818
00:35:28,040 --> 00:35:28,950
Zheng...

819
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:30,320
It's okay.

820
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,840
Wen Yue.

821
00:35:39,470 --> 00:35:40,520
Here, take this back.

822
00:35:57,870 --> 00:35:58,800
Tie Chi, Fei Jian!

823
00:36:01,520 --> 00:36:02,320
Zheng!

824
00:36:06,120 --> 00:36:06,870
Zheng!

825
00:36:14,390 --> 00:36:15,080
Zhao Mo...

826
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:17,630
Zhao Mo...

827
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:20,150
Let's go home.

828
00:36:31,140 --> 00:36:33,020
Look at him, still so young...

829
00:36:33,020 --> 00:36:33,760
Boss,

830
00:36:34,130 --> 00:36:35,130
something's happening over there.

831
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,560
Make way!

832
00:36:48,700 --> 00:36:49,280
Everyone,

833
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:51,040
please remain calm.

834
00:36:51,230 --> 00:36:52,360
Since I've gathered you here,

835
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:54,600
just get your brushes and ink ready.

836
00:36:54,600 --> 00:36:56,560
There's bound to be shocking revelations soon.

837
00:36:56,870 --> 00:36:58,000
What shocking revelations?

838
00:36:58,000 --> 00:36:59,000
We've been waiting forever!

839
00:36:59,050 --> 00:36:59,900
Be patient.

840
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:03,120
Excuse me, make way!

841
00:37:03,710 --> 00:37:04,470
Who's this guy?

842
00:37:05,130 --> 00:37:06,210
You know the Governor, right?

843
00:37:06,210 --> 00:37:06,800
The Governor is here!

844
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:07,910
Didn't I tell you

845
00:37:07,910 --> 00:37:09,040
there'd be big news?

846
00:37:09,470 --> 00:37:10,430
The Governor himself is here!

847
00:37:10,430 --> 00:37:11,470
It must be big!

848
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:12,950
I'm here to watch the play.

849
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:15,800
Why did you seat me on the stage?

850
00:37:16,470 --> 00:37:18,360
Father, trust me.

851
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,430
For this play,

852
00:37:19,430 --> 00:37:21,080
you're sitting in the best seat.

853
00:37:22,600 --> 00:37:23,630
You and your clever ideas!

854
00:37:32,490 --> 00:37:33,400
Here they come!

855
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,630
Everyone knows

856
00:37:41,710 --> 00:37:43,000
that I often tell stories

857
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:44,710
here at the business center.

858
00:37:44,910 --> 00:37:45,580
In the past,

859
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:47,360
I mostly told historical tales.

860
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:48,160
Today,

861
00:37:48,470 --> 00:37:50,640
I'll be inviting a young talent

862
00:37:51,230 --> 00:37:53,430
to join me in recounting

863
00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:55,230
a tale of past secrets.

864
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,710
A tale of past secrets...

865
00:37:57,870 --> 00:38:01,390
Please stay and enjoy the performance.

866
00:38:01,390 --> 00:38:03,950
I thank you all in advance.

867
00:38:07,390 --> 00:38:08,910
Let us welcome this talented guest,

868
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:10,360
Zhao Buyou!

869
00:38:12,390 --> 00:38:13,360
Who's Zhao Buyou?

870
00:38:13,390 --> 00:38:14,120
